WEBVTT

00:05:59.680 --> 00:06:03.256
that are performing
most strongly on TSI --

00:06:03.280 --> 00:06:04.936
total societal impact --

00:06:04.960 --> 00:06:09.240
see a 19 percent premium
on their valuation.

00:06:10.120 --> 00:06:11.360
19 percent.

00:06:11.960 --> 00:06:13.296
When they do really well

00:06:13.320 --> 00:06:16.776
on things like minimizing
the impact of their company

00:06:16.800 --> 00:06:19.096
on the environment and water,

00:06:19.120 --> 00:06:23.200
and when they have very strong
occupational health and safety programs.

00:06:23.880 --> 00:06:28.536
And when they also add in
strong employee training programs,

00:06:28.560 --> 00:06:33.256
they get a 3.4 percentage point
premium on their margins.